<doc id="1078567" wikidata="Q2291528" url="?curid=1078567" title="Singles (Travis album)">
<text>Singles is the first and only compilation album by the Scottish rock band Travis, released on 1 November 2004. The album consists of all of the band&#x27;s singles from 1996 to 2004, as well as including two new tracks, &quot;Walking in the Sun&quot; and &quot;The Distance&quot;. The album charted at number 4 on the UK Albums Chart, performing considerably better than &quot;12 Memories&quot;, selling the required 300,000 copies to make it a Platinum album.

